channel.title: Comments on: Floss Gloss Fall 2013 Princess of the Night Collection Swatches & Review

item.title: By: jenw
item.dc:creator: jenw
item.description: Those all look rad! I want Moon Baby. I always try to find something similar and so far, everything else I've bought only looks good in the bottle and takes a hundred coats to look the same on my nails. Gonna try it!
